{"tid":709311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界盃】日本球迷完場執垃圾　感染他人齊齊清理看台","createTime":"2018-06-20T02:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T04:19:05.000Z","uid":20933,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8726117d595da0d0981346978cd50bcef54e60b3","tid":709311,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180620/s00005/0c38be990812c43d6e0fcf003d58e922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180620%2Fs00005%2F0c38be990812c43d6e0fcf003d58e922.jpg&h=ff460af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本人的公民素質及公德心舉世聞名，在星期二世界盃H組賽事日本對哥倫比亞2：1勝出後，觀賽的日本球迷未有即時離場慶祝，而是留在場內，親自撿走自己製造的垃圾，行動甚至更感染哥倫比亞的球迷加入。<br />\n<br />\n日本球迷4年前在巴西世界盃時，已自備藍色大垃圾袋清理看台的垃圾，今次亦不例外。有俄羅斯網民在社交網站上載影片，見一眾日本球迷留在現場，拿着藍色垃圾袋清理看台，今次舉動更感染在場的哥倫比亞球迷，大家齊齊清理垃圾，影片成為網上熱話。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》的報道形容，「日本再次展示他們在擁有最佳的世界盃球迷，他們戰勝哥倫比亞留在看台清理，上屆敗給科特迪瓦時，他們也有這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1183816301/videos/10214244779691776/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1183816301%2Fvideos%2F10214244779691776%2F&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=19aaedf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1183816301/videos/10214244779691776/</a>"},{"pid":"aa100dee51006babdf6472eff19d71dfdfb8b579","tid":709311,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180620/s00005/1529458562650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180620%2Fs00005%2F1529458562650&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c6c41576\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180620%2Fs00005%2F1529458562650&h=4dc33877\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla